snippet.title: Welcome to Fortnite: MEGA Intro Trailer
snippet.description:
Watch the Fortnite Chapter 4 Season 2 MEGA Intro Trailer and for more details visit https://www.fortnite.com/

Artist: ATARASHII GAKKO!
Title: WOO! GO!

The Fortnite Chapter 4 Season 2 Battle Pass includes the Thunder Outfit and more. Reach level 100 and you can earn:

Mizuki Outfit
Thunder Outfit
Imani Outfit
Stray Outfit
Renzo the Destroyer Outfit
Mystica Outfit
Highwire Outfit
